      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"4. EXCAVATOR TICKET dropped out early but wound up strongly and charged to a strong win by a neck (26.78) at this track in Grade 5. Great chance again. 5. SHADY LADY filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Big Duke (26.62) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to be in this for a long way. 2. IDRON BALE has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 2nd at this track over 460m. The form out of last race has been strong. Will give a great sight again. 7. RUTH'S COMMANDER can feature with the right run.\",\"runners\":[4,5,2,7],\"exclusive\":false}",
